snippet.textDisplay:
The one about adding new Try Guys was interesting in how it correlated with the friendship one. I've wondered about that in the past, because it's felt a little like Miles was becoming an honorary Try Guy, at least. But I realize that the official title reflects on the 4 of them and their bonding over the initial Tries they did together. The only other thing I can think of, off the top of my head, would be like Smosh. I know they were started by two guys, but now they've got a whole crew and one of the OG guys left, yet I see everyone still there as "Smosh".
I guess as long as the OG 4 are together they don't need to official add a new Try Guy. Keep doing stuff with cast/crew, though, and if one or more of them ends up having to leave for whatever (knock on wood) reason then I could see adding new people to the Try Guys.
